entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You've spoken with the Sulfur Lake Pirate ambassador.
entries.journal_entry_description: Speak with the pirate ambassador to negotiate peace between Nym and the Sulfur Lake Pirates.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Act as Nym's emissary and see what peace can be negotiated with the Sulfur Lake Pirates.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: I'd rather not see innocents die but I will not hand over Choster. You need to figure something out.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Henchmen sent to kill you.
entries.task03_utterance_wave_2: Oh a tough guy, huh?! I'll show you.
entries.task03_utterance_wave_3: You may have beaten the others, but not me!
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Speak with the ambassador for the Sulfur Lake Pirates again. See if he changes his tune.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: I would have preferred to thank you in person, but Nym has me in hiding.Thank you so much for having me released.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Return to Nym for your reward.
